{"tid":1018204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲仔景泰苑墮樓　送院不治","createTime":"2019-02-12T05:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T06:01:56.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df52b9f055549e86c51930221dd62505a27f6f02","tid":1018204,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"今日(12日)早上9時17分，新蒲崗景福街118號景泰苑，一名年約20歲男子從高處墮下，飛墮大廈平台奄奄一息，街坊見狀報警求助，消防到場將昏迷事主救回地面，再由救護車送院搶救，惜告不治。據悉，事主姓謝(27歲)，有工作，與家人居住油麻地區，警方正調查事主在上址墮樓原因。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIunKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=1415a17f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190212/mobile/bkn-20190212093438206-0212_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190212%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190212093438206-0212_00822_001.html&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIunKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=891fcd93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190212/mobile/bkn-20190212093438206-0212_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e941a9a6e90e995bd87948961d21d14cadb8cf8","tid":1018204,"uid":30578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"jump jump jump<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbdcb0f751e1bafb2a328e48b76404d8392f05b","tid":1018204,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"祝來生不用做支那人"},{"pid":"bf91875eccb5b8c5cc7650320d0e17d7cc8aa90a","tid":1018204,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcbdcb